Name: dogpet
About the game: Play as a floating pair of hands petting dogs on a floating green meadow. Collect dogpet points by petting your dogs and use them to buy even more dogs to pet. Battle your own excitement as your hands flop around uncontrollably and try to throw you off of the map. Featuring three music tracks.
